            "value": "The Desikan Killiany atlas is based on an automated labeling system for subdividing the human cerebral cortex on magnetic resonance images into gyral based regions of interest. The MNI parcellations provided here are computed by nonlinear registration of the standard parcellation in fsaverage space, using the registration procedure by Wu et al. 2018"
